About YRF Spy Universe:
YRF Spy Universe is a first of its kind cinematic universe of spy thriller films in India. The first film in the universe, "Ek Tha Tiger," starring Salman Khan and Katrina Kaif was released in 2012, followed by its sequel "Tiger Zinda Hai" in 2017. The third film in the universe, "War" was released in 2019 and starred Hrithik Roshan and Tiger Shroff in pivotal roles. "Pathaan" was the fourth instalment in the Spy Universe franchise which was released in 2023 starring Shah Rukh Khan, Deepika Padukone and John Abraham. "Tiger 3", the fifth instalment in the YRF Spy Universe and the third film in the Tiger series, starring Salman Khan, Katrina Kaif and Emraan Hashmi, released in 2023. "War 2", the sixth film in the YRF Spy Universe, starring Hrithik Roshan, NTR and Kiara Advani, directed by Ayan Mukerji, released on 14 August 2025. "Alpha", the seventh film in the franchise and Hindi cinema‚Äôs first female-led YRF Spy Universe film, starring Alia Bhatt and Sharvari, will release on 25 December 2025.

snippet.title: Rippan Swaamy Official Trailer | Vijay Raghavendra | Ashwini Chandrashekar | Kishor Mudubidire | PRK
snippet.description:
Panchaanana Films productions in association with PRK Audio
presents
Rippan Swaamy - A rural thriller set in the fictional Malnad village of Snana Kopa.
The story unfolds after the mysterious suicide of Rippan Swaamy, leading to a trail of secrets, drama, and suspense. As the mystery deepens, the truth behind his name and death slowly unravels.

The film is set to release in theatres on August 29.
 üéµ Listen to the soulful songs exclusively on PRK Audio.

The story unfolds after the mysterious suicide of Rippan Swaamy, leading to a trail of secrets, drama, and suspense. As the mystery deepens, the truth behind his name and death slowly unravels.

The film is set to release in theatres on August 29.

snippet.description:
White Hill Dhaakad Presents
üî• CHEETE ‚Äì Masoom Sharma ka dhamakedaar comeback! üî•

üéß Gaana: https://gaana.com/song/cheete-4


üëÅÔ∏è‚Äçüó®Ô∏è Lyrics :
Ham balak dil ke cheete se
Jo kheli baji jeete se
Jo khud ne keh de daage re
Wo bhaja bhaja ke peete se 
Kad dekhe cheete girte re
Kad dekhe cheete marte re
Kutte billi gandu te kade 
Dekhe cheete darte re 
Kai hockey te tode se
Kaiyan ke mare beete se
Mahre 100 te upar hoye mukadme sare jeete se
Ham balak dil ke cheete se
Jo kheli baji jeete se
Jo khud ne keh ke daagee re
Wo bhaja bhaja je peete sai
Ham balak dil ke cheete sai

Ham gama aale baalak se
Ham kaama aale baalak se
Koi or nahi jine murder kara 
Mere mama aale balak se
Chaati pe gode dhar diye jange
Khoon me bode kar diye jange
Jo seedhe anty dahiya ne  
Chock pe kode kar diye jange
Chock pe kode kar diye jange
Tadke karke full chale  
Sanjh ne hoja reete se
Jinki naad me sariya tha
Un ne mare bande feeke se
Ham baalak dil ke cheete se
Jo kheli baji jeete sai
Jo khud ne keh ke daage re
Wo bhaja bhaja je peete se
Ham baalak dil ke cheete se

Ham baalak pak pavitar re
Mahra chand te saaf charitar re
Yare pyare gadi me 
Na rakhi mahila mitar re
Na marte badda vendor re
Ek khet me khadi defender re
Delhi me bande maran ka hamne le rakha tender re
Hamne le rakha tender re
Kai chhat te niche baga diye
Kai gadi gel gasite se
Raja they raja se maade din bhi maare ache beete se
Ham baalak dil ke cheete se
Jo kheli baji jeete sai
Jo khud ne keh ke daage re 
Wo bhaja bhaja je peete se
Ham baalak dil ke cheete se

Japan is fractured into many independent nations entangled in ceaseless war. At the center lies Ashina, a land of sacred earth and ancient mystery. Two decades after Sword Saint Isshin Ashina reclaimed the region in a brutal coup, a new threat emerges from within: The Interior Ministry. Desperate to protect his homeland, Isshin‚Äôs grandson Genichiro turns to forbidden powers. About T-Series Fox 

On our channel we create –∞ trailer mashups ‚ñ∑
Also known as recut trailers, involve collecting multiple pieces of film footage from one or multiple movies and Add Our Own Dialogues To Make A New And Fresh Story, editing them to create a new trailer. Trailer mashups are often created for a movie that does not exist now or to change the genre of an existing film. These are derivative works as defined by the United States Copyright Act 17 U.S.C. ¬ß 101, and as such, may find protection from copyright claims under the doctrine of fair use.

The trailer mashups are not only a user generated form of digital creativity but a way to create anticipation for future releases, working in tandem with current movie trailers. Movie trailers are designed to give minimal plot detail and to create hype and anticipation. Fan made trailer mashups allow the audience to perform their own cinematic spin on current movie footage. This allows the trailer to focus on a specific actor or portion of the film. It could even change the plot ocr genre of the film entirely.

This video is a parody DUE to its derivative/ transformative nature this video is covered as a Fair Use of material.
